<methods><methodStep><description><section>
<title>Acquiring the dataset</title>
<para>I obtained the United States dam locations from the USGS data distribution web site. 

I obtained the HUC polygons from the National Hydrological Dataset (enhanced edition) produced for the US EPA by private contractor Horizons Systems, Inc and available to the scientific community. I assigned polygon attributes to each dam location point using an R script described below. </para>
</section></description></methodStep>
