<samplingDescription>
<para>We used an R script that implemented a Point-In-Polygon algorithm to assign the surrounding HUC-8 watershed polygon to each dam point location. The script is packaged with the component datasets in a compressed (zip) archive file available from the NCEAS Data Repository.</para>
</samplingDescription>
